reviewText: Was okay.shipped fast..just wasn't what I thought it was
Very well done . I saw this first on the History Channel and wanted for my collection
Good documentary on UFOs and their cover up.  I would recommend this to anyone interested in expanding their knowledge on this subject.

Conspiracy?? You decide. A lot of factual information and a "oh really?" DVD. Well worth the money and your time. You might want to have pen and paper so you can "jot" down information or any questions.  It is very definitely worth your time. And if nothing else, you know more now than you did before you watched the DVD!! I certainly did!!!
